COVID-19 cases worldwide now at 8.3 million; 
Southeast Asia records more than 540,000 COVID-19 cases; 
Total confirmed COVID-19 cases in the Philippines reaches 28,459; recoveries now at 7,378; 1,130 deaths; 
North Central Luzon records 909 COVID-19 positive cases; 82 deaths; 
Bicol Region records 86 COVID-19 positive cases;  5 deaths 
Central Visayas records 5,604 COVID-19 positive cases; 151 deaths; 
Eastern Visayas records 344 COVID-19 positive cases with no deaths; 
Western Visayas records 164 COVID-19 positive cases; 11 deaths 
Mindanao records 895 covid-19 positive cases; 50 deaths



